title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Ryan Navion - version 1.0
description:
The Ryan Navion has been released yesterday and is a small aircraft which has been created by B4Gunner. The aircraft comes with a small document describing the aircraft details and a checklist which can be used to operate the aircraft. The aircraft is still under development and currently both the radio and navigation features are not working yet. 

0:00 intro video
0:11: start of exterior and cockpit review
04:56 trying to start the engines
12:00 take off and perform a short flight

The latest version of the aircraft can be downloaded from flightsim.to:
https://flightsim.to/file/23285/ryan-navion
